s/post/473b4cb31774", "anchor_text": "salience method"}, {"url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramer%E2%80%93Douglas%E2%80%93Peucker_algorithm", "anchor_text": "Ramer\u2013Douglas\u2013Peucker algorithm"}, {"url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramer%E2%80%93Douglas%E2%80%93Peucker_algorithm", "anchor_text": "Source"}, {"url": "https://www.researchgate.net/publication/224623408_Determining_independent_grasp_regions_on_2D_discrete_objects", "anchor_text": "some algorithms"}, {"url": "https://github.com/TimChinenov/GraspPicture", "anchor_text": "TimChinenov/GraspPictureCode for segmenting salient colored images and determining a grasp. - TimChinenov/GraspPicturegithub.com"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/tag/programming?source=post_page-----9e91c239b329---------------programming-----------------", "anchor_text": "Programming"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/tag/computer-vision?source=post_page-----9e91c239b329---------------computer_vision-----------------", "anchor_text": "Computer Vision"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/tag/software-development?source=post_page-----9e91c239b329---------------software_development-----------------", "anchor_text": "Software Development"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/tag/projects?source=post_page-----9e91c239b329---------------projects-----------------", "anchor_text": "Projects"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/tag/computer-science?source=post_page-----9e91c239b329---------------computer_science-----------------", "anchor_text": "Computer Science"}, {"url": "https://medium.com/m/signin?actionUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F_%2Fvote%2Ftowards-data-science%2F9e91c239b329&operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Ftowardsdatascience.com%2Fdiscretizing-2d-images-into-polygonal-and-point-models-9e91c239b329&user=Tim+Chinenov&userId=d8ef4d6fe020&source=-----9e91c239b329---------------------clap_footer-----------", "anchor_text": ""}, {"url": "https://medium.com/m/signin?actionUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F_%2Fvote%2Ftowards-data-science%2F9e91c239b3